Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and disclose your information when you use our mobile applications (the “Apps”).
Information We Collect:
We might collect two types of information:
Personal Information:
This includes information that can be used to identify you, such as your name, address, date of birth, email address, or phone number. You may be required to provide some personal information to use certain features of the Apps. The application will inform you if any information of this type might be required.
Device Information:
We may collect information about your device, such as its model, operating system version, and unique identifiers. This information is used to improve the functionality of the Apps.
How We Use Your Information:
We use your information for the following purposes:
To provide and improve the Apps
To personalize your experience
To communicate with you
To analyze how the Apps are used
To comply with legal obligations
Your Choices:
You can withdraw your consent to our collection and use of your personal information at any time by contacting us at admin[at]rayadams.app. We will delete your personal information within five business days of receiving your request.
Location Information:
If any of our Apps require access to your device’s GPS location, we will only use that data within the App and will not store it anywhere without your permission.
Sharing Your Information:
We do not share your personal information with any third parties.
Security:
We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no internet transmission or electronic storage is 100% secure.
Embedded Content:
The Apps may include embedded content from other websites. These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, and track your interaction with the embedded content. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these websites.
Changes to this Policy:
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post the changes on our website and in the Apps.
Contact Us:
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at admin[at]rayadams.app.
Last update: June 3, 2024
